==反響==
===收視及欣賞指數===
如不把聖誕特輯計算在內，《史密斯與瓊斯》是整個系列中收看人數最多的一集，節目在首播時英國共有871萬觀看<ref name="rating">{{cite journal | journal=Doctor Who Magazine |date=August 2007 | issue=386|pages=6}}</ref>。整個系列的平均收看人數是754萬人，[[收視率|收視率]]介於37%至41%，累積觀看人數達3千萬人<ref name="rating"/>。[[欣賞指數|欣賞指數]]方面，每集均在85分以上<ref name="AI">{{cite web|title=Ratings Guide|url=http://guide.doctorwhonews.net/info.php?detail=ratings&type=date|website=Doctor Who News|accessdate=2014-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018011335/http://guide.doctorwhonews.net/info.php?detail=ratings&type=date|archive-date=2015-10-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。當中，《史密斯與瓊斯》和《最後的時間領主》同樣獲得88分，是這個系列中得分最高的兩集<ref name="AI"/>。

===專業評價===
《[[IGN|IGN]]》的布林伯格在10分為滿分下給了這個系列9分。他大讚[[大衛·田納特|大衛·田納特]]、[[費馬·阿吉曼|費馬·阿吉曼]]和約翰·森「神乎其技」的演出，又用「傑作」來形容整個系列，更相信沒有其它劇作能跟它比下去<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2007/11/07/doctor-who-the-complete-third-series-dvd-review?page=2 |title=Doctor Who - The Complete Third Series DVD Review - IGN |publisher=Uk.ign.com |date=7-11-2007 |accessdate=2014-08-23}}</ref>。《DVD Talk》的尼克·里昂斯在5星為滿分下給這個系列4星半，認為這系列與之前的兩個系列同樣出色，並指鐘斯這角和整個系列都「不會讓觀眾失望」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/31196/doctor-who-the-complete-third-series/ |title=Doctor Who - The Complete Third Series : DVD Talk Review of the DVD Video |publisher=Dvdtalk.com |date= |accessdate=2014-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140822013336/http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/31196/doctor-who-the-complete-third-series/ |archive-date=2014-08-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

系列中的數集被影評家視為經典。《[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]》的加文·費特、凱瑟琳·吉和本·勞倫斯在{{link-en|異世奇人 (系列9)|Doctor Who (Series 9)|系列9}}播出前選出10部最棒的新版《異世奇人》故事，《人性》/《血之家族》合集以及《眨眼》位列第4和第1<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/doctor-who/11495607/10-best-modern-era-Doctor-Who-episodes.html|title=10 best modern-era Doctor Who episodes|publisher=Telegraph.co.uk|date=2015-09-19|accessdate=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006230430/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/doctor-who/11495607/10-best-modern-era-Doctor-Who-episodes.html|archive-date=2015-10-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。報章《Metro》點列出10部一定要觀看的《異世奇人》劇集，《人性》和《眨眼》位列其中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://metro.co.uk/2015/03/19/doctor-who-10th-anniversary-10-must-watch-new-who-episodes-human-nature-5106630/|title=Doctor Who 10th anniversary: 10 must watch new Who episodes – Human Nature|publisher=Metro.co.uk|date=2015-03-19|accessdate=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926105219/http://metro.co.uk/2015/03/19/doctor-who-10th-anniversary-10-must-watch-new-who-episodes-human-nature-5106630/|archive-date=2015-09-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://metro.co.uk/2015/03/19/doctor-who-10th-anniversary-10-must-watch-new-who-episodes-human-nature-5106630/|title=Doctor Who 10th anniversary: 10 must watch new Who episodes – Blink|publisher=Metro.co.uk|date=2015-03-19|accessdate=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926105219/http://metro.co.uk/2015/03/19/doctor-who-10th-anniversary-10-must-watch-new-who-episodes-human-nature-5106630/|archive-date=2015-09-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《Short List》雜誌列出20部最好的舊版和新版《異世奇人》劇集，《逃跑的新娘》和《眨眼》進入名單之中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.shortlist.com/entertainment/tv/the-20-best-doctor-who-episodes-ever|title=The 20 best Doctor Who episodes ever|publisher=Shortlist.com|date=|accessdate=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924005639/http://www.shortlist.com/entertainment/tv/the-20-best-doctor-who-episodes-ever|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《烏托邦》留下的懸念令影評家有深刻印象。《io9》的{{link-en|查理·珍·安德絲|Charlie Jane Anders}}指《烏托邦》是她最愛的懸念<ref>{{cite web|first=Charlie Jane|last=Anders|url=http://io9.com/5625151/greatest-doctor-who-cliffhangers-of-all-time|title=Greatest Doctor Who cliffhangers of all time!|publisher=io9|date=2010-08-31|accessdate=2012-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120514031149/http://io9.com/5625151/greatest-doctor-who-cliffhangers-of-all-time|archive-date=2012-05-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《What Culture》的克里斯汀·布恩在2014年選出15個最扣人心弦的《異世奇人》懸念，這集位列第7，並被誇讚為「大師級典範」<ref>{{cite web|first=Christian|last=Bone|url=http://whatculture.com/tv/15-greatest-doctor-who-cliffhangers-of-all-time.php/10|title=15 Greatest Doctor Who Cliffhangers Of All Time|work=What Culture|date=2-12-2014|accessdate=10-9-2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304114205/http://whatculture.com/tv/15-greatest-doctor-who-cliffhangers-of-all-time.php/10|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。《[[衛報|衛報]]》的史堤芬·布克在評論整個系列3時寫稱：「這懸念也許是個系列中最精彩的一刻」<ref>{{cite web|first=Stephen|last=Brook|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/organgrinder/2007/jul/02/doctorwhoitsseasonfinalet|title=Doctor Who: it's season finale time!|work=The Guardian|date=2-7-2007|accessdate=2012-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103224409/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/organgrinder/2007/jul/02/doctorwhoitsseasonfinalet|archive-date=2012-11-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

於《眨眼》中出現的怪物哭泣天使獲得廣泛的好評。《SFX》於2009年選出21大《異世奇人》中最恐怖的劇集，《眨眼》位列榜首，筆者評論道﹕「一頭在你看不到的時候才會動的怪物已夠可怕，而在閃爍的燈光和斷斷續續的配樂親托下，場面變得更嚇人」<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.sfx.co.uk/2009/02/01/21_scariest_doctor_who_moments_7/|title=21 Scariest Doctor Who Moments 7|journal=SFX|publisher=Future Publishing|date=1-2-2009|accessdate=2012-04-14|author=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141109144805/http://www.sfx.co.uk/2009/02/01/21_scariest_doctor_who_moments_7/|archive-date=2014-11-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。作家[[尼爾·蓋曼|尼爾·蓋曼]]在《[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]》評選10個最經典的新怪物，哭泣天使排名第3<ref>{{Cite news|title=Neil Gaiman: My Top 10 New Classic Monsters|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/galler/0,,20213067_20213322_20214359_3,00.html|newspaper=Entertainment Weekly|publisher=Time Inc|date=7/2008|accessdate=7-8-2012}}</ref>。與此同時，《TV Squad》也把這外星生物評為電視史上最可怕怪物的第3位<ref>{{cite web|first=Annie|last=Wu|url=http://www.aoltv.com/2007/10/24/all-time-scariest-tv-characters-3-weeping-angels/|title=All-time scariest TV characters|work=TV Squad|publisher=Weblogs, Inc|date=2007-10-24|accessdate=7-8-2012|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gs4xFzdl?url=http://www.aoltv.com/2007/10/24/all-time-scariest-tv-characters-3-weeping-angels/|archive-date=2013-05-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

雖然這系列取得好評，節目還是受到一些批評。史堤芬·占士·獲加在其著作《未官方及未授權的異世奇人指南2007》（The Unofficial and Unauthorised Guide to Doctor Who 2007）對《最後的時間領主》中時光倒流的劇情感到不滿，認為這和「按下重置鍵」無異。<ref>{{cite book|author=Walker, Stephen James|title=Third Dimension: The Unofficial and Unauthorised Guide to Doctor Who 2007|url=https://archive.org/details/thirddimensionun0000walk|publisher=Telos Publishing|year=2007|pages=[https://archive.org/details/thirddimensionun0000walk/page/264 264]|isbn=978-1-84583-016-8}}</ref>。對此，戴維斯不同意，認為在時光倒流後，博士和法師等人的命連徹底改變，跟「重置」是正正相反的<ref name="dwm386"/>。

===獎項及榮譽===
這個系列贏得多個獎項。史蒂芬·莫法特憑《眨眼》問鼎2008年度的[[英國電影和電視藝術學院|英國電影和電視藝術學院]]最佳編劇獎，[[馬瑞·高德|馬瑞·高德]]和BBC威爾士音效組分別提名為最佳電視原創配音及最佳音效獎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/7395593.stm |title=Entertainment | Bafta glory for Channel 4's Boy A |publisher=BBC News |date=2008-05-12 |accessdate=2014-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080517174026/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/7395593.stm |archive-date=2008-05-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。歐內斯德·華斯爾獲得威爾斯電影和電視藝術學院最佳攝影指導獎。{{link-en|路絲·派殊|Louise Page}}、尼爾·哥頓和希拉格·維斯憑《勇救莎翁》取得最佳服飾獎及最佳化妝獎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/pressreleases/stories/2008/04_april/28/cymru.shtml |title=Press Office - BAFTA Cymru success for BBC Wales |publisher=BBC |date=2008-04-28 |accessdate=2014-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160220114156/http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/pressreleases/stories/2008/04_april/28/cymru.shtml |archive-date=2016-02-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在{{link-en|星座獎|Constellation Awards}}方面，戴維斯憑《人性》/《血之家族》合集贏得最佳男子表現獎，《眨眼》的主角[[嘉莉·慕萊根|嘉莉·慕萊根]]取得最佳女主角獎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://constellations.tcon.ca/2008.shtml |title=The Constellation Awards - A Canadian Award for Excellence in Film & Television Science Fiction |publisher=Constellations.tcon.ca |date=2014-07-08 |accessdate=2014-08-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140726122405/http://constellations.tcon.ca/2008.shtml |archivedate=2014-07-26 }}</ref>。在2007年舉辦的愛丁堡國際電視節，這系列奪取年度最佳節目獎<ref>{{cite web|last=Young |first=Kevin |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/6963958.stm |title=Entertainment | BBC One wins channel of the year |publisher=BBC News |date=2007-08-25 |accessdate=2014-08-23}}</ref>。在另一個於[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]主辦的頒獎禮中，戴維斯獲頒授格蘭菲迪精神獎<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.scotsman.com/news/scotland/top-stories/top-scot-dedicates-award-to-his-little-angel-1-701904 |title=Top Scot dedicates award to his 'little angel' |publisher=The Scotsman |date=2007-11-30 |accessdate=2014-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150203131518/http://www.scotsman.com/news/scotland/top-stories/top-scot-dedicates-award-to-his-little-angel-1-701904 |archive-date=2015-02-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2008年度的[[雨果獎|雨果獎]]，《眨眼》和《人性》/《血之家族》進入最佳戲劇表現獎的最終候選名單，這獎項最後由《眨眼》奪得<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yVVJFbu3?url=http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/2008-hugo-awards/ |archivedate=2011-05-07 |title=2008 Hugo Awards |publisher=http://www.thehugoawards.org/ |url=http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/2008-hugo-awards/ |date= |accessdate=2014-08-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。同時，系列3在第13屆[[國家電視獎|國家電視獎]]問鼎最受歡迎節目獎、田納特獲得最受歡迎男主角獎，而阿吉曼則被提名為最受歡迎女主角<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/news/a77730/doctor-who-leads-tv-awards-nominees.html#~oNv4pN5OpnpLU6 |title='Doctor Who' leads TV Awards nominees - TV News |publisher=Digital Spy |date=2007-10-15 |accessdate=2014-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714154351/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/news/a77730/doctor-who-leads-tv-awards-nominees.html#~oNv4pN5OpnpLU6 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/7072109.stm |title=Entertainment | Winners in full: National TV Awards |publisher=BBC News |date=2007-10-31 |accessdate=2014-08-23}}</ref>。

此外，莫法特憑《眨眼》獲提名為[[星雲獎|星雲獎]]的最佳劇本獎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://dpsinfo.com/awardweb/nebulas/00s.html |title=Nebula Award Final Ballots from the 2000s |publisher=Dpsinfo.com |date= |accessdate=2014-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20011202011002/http://dpsinfo.com/awardweb/nebulas/00s.html |archive-date=2001-12-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 。在{{link-en|蒙地卡羅電視節| Monte-Carlo Television Festival}}中，阿吉曼和戴維斯被提名為傑出表現獎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://entertainment.msn.com/photos/gallery2.aspx?gallery=15278 |title=2007 Monte Carlo Television Festival - "Doctor Who" Freema Agyeman Photocall - Movies |publisher=Entertainment.msn.com |date= |accessdate=2014-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821073314/http://entertainment.msn.com/photos/gallery2.aspx?gallery=15278 |archive-date=2014-08-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。同時，這系列還獲提名為2007年度[[尖叫獎|尖叫獎]]的最佳電視節目獎<ref>{{cite web |author=Ryan Turek |url=http://www.shocktillyoudrop.com/news/1268-scream-award-nominees-announced/ |title=Scream Award Nominees Announced |publisher=Shock Till You Drop |date=2007-09-05 |accessdate=2014-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906040916/http://www.shocktillyoudrop.com/news/1268-scream-award-nominees-announced/ |archive-date=2014-09-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在同年的TV Quick頒獎禮中，系列3和田納特分別獲最愛劇集獎及最佳男主角獎，阿吉曼被提名為最佳女主角<ref>{{cite web |last=Parker |first=Robin |url=http://www.broadcastnow.co.uk/corrie-cleans-up-at-tv-quick-awards/121375.article |title=Corrie cleans up at TV Quick awards | News | Broadcast |publisher=Broadcastnow.co.uk |date=2007-09-04 |accessdate=2014-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222162640/http://www.broadcastnow.co.uk/corrie-cleans-up-at-tv-quick-awards/121375.article |archive-date=2014-02-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另外，負責《最後的時間領主》的美術組獲提名為2008年視覺效果協會獎的傑出視覺效果獎以及傑出人物動畫獎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.visualeffectssociety.com/awards/ves?field_aw_year_tid=57 |title=Previous VES Awards |publisher=Visual Effects Society |date= |accessdate=2014-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821100639/http://www.visualeffectssociety.com/awards/ves?field_aw_year_tid=57 |archive-date=2014-08-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。英國作家協會向系列3的編劇頒授最佳劇作獎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.doctorwhonews.net/2012/09/nominations-announced-for-writers-guild.html |title=Nominations Announced For Writers' Guild Awards 2012 |publisher=Doctor Who News |date= |accessdate=2014-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821110949/http://www.doctorwhonews.net/2012/09/nominations-announced-for-writers-guild.html |archive-date=2014-08-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

